did.unittitle: John and Jenny Mae Notebooks, p. 1-72 and p. 1-136

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents note
scopecontent.p: Notebooks appear to be related as part of a lengthy manuscript, which takes place in an urban setting with mentions of street cars as well as a tuberculosis hospital. Smaller notebook contains a brief journal entry dated May 16, 1979. Pages 63-72 of the smaller notebook have been photocopied and placed in Belle notebooks (Box 44, Folder 11).
